クラス NoRecordException

  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    Serializable

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public class NoRecordException
extends RegistryIOException
    Raised if there is no ServiceRecord resolved at the end of the specified path.

    There may be valid data of some form at the end of the path, but it does not appear to be a Service Record.
